name: Mr Burn
body:
Located on a beautiful hill surrounded by lush green tropical forest with lots of greeneries, fresh air and negative ions needed for a healthy living environment.

Condo with full facilities and 24 hours security personnels on rounds. Clubhouse with a massive size event hall, Olympic size swimmimg pool, squash court, a big gym with full equipments available to sweat out from 9.00am - 9.00pm, 7 days a week, jogging tracks, children playground as well as 2 squash courts.

Schools available for government as well as private international within minutes drive from the condo. Nearby, a small township of Alam Jaya foodcourt and shopping area with provision shops, supermarket, clinics, laundry outlet etc, etc also available.

Easy road access to Hulu Langat, Kajang Highway, Taman Connaught, Batu 9,Taman Suntex, Taman Ceupacs, Taman Mudun ( Econsave Supermarket ) and the rest of several other Tamans. Batu 9 MRT is about 10 mins. drive from the condo by bus or own transport.

Description:
Situated along Jalan Stapok Utama there are retail shops on the lower floors which are great to serve the residentsâ€™ immediate convenience and necessities. the homes are able to accommodate singles and also families, as the smallest unit has 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, whilst the biggest units has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Additionally, the residents are able to use facilities such as the indoor gym, BBQ area, swimming pool, steam room, and enjoy the peaceful landscaped garden. HK Square is adjacent to residential areas that include Royal Garden, Taman Seri Emas , Rancangan Perumahan Batu Kawa, Everbright Estate, and Batu Kawa amongst others. Other than that, there are a few condominium and apartment projects close by, and commercial and retail shops that are quite convenient as well. Schools nearby include Sunny Hill School, SJK Chung Hua No. 6, Sekolah Kebangsaan Garland, and amenities such as the Sarawak General Hospital, Balai Polis Sg.
